    ReviewSession --> SkillReview : contains
    ReviewSession --> ReverseReview : receives feedback
    ReviewSession --> ReviewEvidence : stores evidence
    SkillReview --> FlaggedReview : may be flagged
    ReviewSession --> TaskSelfAssessment : reviewee reflection

    ReviewSession --> ReviewSessionEntity : mapped to domain
    SkillReview --> SkillReviewEntity : mapped to domain
    ReviewRepository ..> ReviewSessionEntity : loads
